{"tid":551282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"beyond首冷雨夜係咪寫比林過雲？","createTime":"2018-02-05T13:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T18:18:06.000Z","uid":136773,"like":10,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f9b5379239eeb76f7187b25636fa38f7617d15","tid":551282,"uid":136773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/211747_69a799247eda06deb1d3512c407a730e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F211747_69a799247eda06deb1d3512c407a730e.jpg&h=4a8b14a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林過雲在犯案前為一名值夜班的的士司機，而案件中受害者均為女性。犯案時多為下雨的晚上，他以的士把目標接載到僻靜地方後勒死，並對第四名受害者進行姦屍。林把屍體的性器官部份肢解作為標本，存放在位於土瓜灣貴州街安慶大廈2樓F室的寓所。<br />\n<br />\n第四名受害者梁惠心，學生，17歲。她於1982年7月2日在尖沙咀參加謝師宴，晚上11時在酒店門外等候的士時，上了林過雲所駕駛的的士。林過雲說，梁惠心是與他相處最久的死者。他殺死對方之前，逼她戴上手銬，與她在的士內交談了很久，內容都是有關學校、前途、家庭、宗教、靈魂等等。但是，最後林過雲還是選擇用電線勒死她，然後將她的屍體帶回去姦屍，是唯一一個被林過雲姦屍的受害者，再進行肢解拍照錄影。錄影帶名為「第四次行動」，殘肢棄於銅鑼灣大坑道山坡草叢。<br />\n<br />\n1982年2月至7月殺害4名女子，每次作案後均會肢解人體、拍攝殘肢、製成標本，並拿去一間沖曬店沖曬，同年8月18日於尖沙咀一沖曬店被捕。案件1983年3月3日在高等法院開審[2]。他最終被判死刑，但因香港已廢除死刑，他於1984年8月依照慣例改判終身監禁，而他已由赤柱監獄轉往石壁監獄服刑。長期監禁刑罰覆核委員會在考慮大眾的關注和憂慮下，決定不會假釋林過雲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在雨中漫步 藍色街燈漸露<br />\n相對望 無聲緊擁抱著<br />\n為了找往日 尋溫馨的往日 消失了<br />\n<br />\n任雨灑我面 難分水點淚痕<br />\n心更亂 愁絲繞千百段<br />\n驟變的態度 無心傷她說話 收不了<br />\n<br />\n冷雨夜我在你身邊<br />\n盼望你會知 可知道我的心<br />\n比當初已改變 只牽強地相處<br />\n冷雨夜我不想歸家<br />\n怕望你背影 只苦笑望雨點<br />\n須知要說清楚 可是我沒膽試<br />\n<br />\n在雨中漫步 嘗水中的味道<br />\n彷似是 情此刻的盡時<br />\n未了解結合 留低思憶片段 不經意<br />\n<br />\n冷雨夜我在你身邊<br />\n盼望你會知 可知道我的心<br />\n比當初已改變 只牽強地相處<br />\n冷雨夜我不想歸家<br />\n怕望你背影 只苦笑望雨點<br />\n須知要說清楚 可是我沒膽試<br />\n<br />\n冷雨夜我在你身邊<br />\n盼望你會知 可知道我的心<br />\n比當初已改變 只牽強地相處<br />\n冷雨夜我不想歸家<br />\n怕望你背影 只苦笑望雨點<br />\n須知要說清楚 可是我沒膽試"},{"pid":"110d14e235f45f190670410ff6c90603d344f8c5","tid":551282,"uid":116530,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"你想像力太好姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e27c33db5436fe62479f29f2ed37d110e9bde4a","tid":551282,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0dcb77300c36686046ed737c2510a1041e564d","tid":551282,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"首歌邊年"},{"pid":"b1e1f5ff1136bfc70f36d16c524cccdda742b8c4","tid":551282,"uid":60959,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"你侮辱咗首歌"},{"pid":"47e704546f18e2099b4e0556528dfac091a3593d","tid":551282,"uid":136773,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你侮辱咗首歌</blockquote><br />\n1986年香港殿堂級搖滾樂隊Beyond成員黃家駒，當年為了探索林過雲的思路歷程及對死亡的抽象，創作出了一首叫《Dead romance part2》的歌曲 ，歌詞It's a rainy night/Can you help me/Man, you feel so lonely(這雨夜,你可否來給我救援,你多孤獨),探索了「雨夜屠夫」的心路歷程。<br />\n<br />\n冷雨夜發行於1988年專輯「再見理想」 ﹐歌詞最後一句 <br />\n：雖知要說清楚 可惜我沒膽試"},{"pid":"4929d466a89ecc2b1c905ba9c5864b6a7e493df4","tid":551282,"uid":136773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你侮辱咗首歌</blockquote><br />\n1986年香港殿堂級搖滾樂隊Beyond成員黃家駒，當年為了探索林過雲的思路歷程及對死亡的抽象，創作出了一首叫《Dead romance part2》的歌曲 ，歌詞It's a rainy night/Can you help me/Man, you feel so lonely(這雨夜,你可否來給我救援,你多孤獨),探索了「雨夜屠夫」的心路歷程。<br />\n<br />\n冷雨夜發行於1988年專輯「<del>再見理想</del>現代舞台」 ﹐歌詞最後一句 <br />\n：雖知要說清楚 可惜我沒膽試</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1986年「再見理想」是香港搖滾樂隊Beyond第一張自資粵語專輯。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=105sM7_ZMT4&amp;feature=related\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D105sM7_ZMT4%26feature%3Drelated&d=A8E5SHWKOxCGSy%2BODRUFMU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=779535dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=105sM7_ZMT4&amp;feature=related</a>"},{"pid":"2b448c72cf79e02567d345e67d136a25cb56641f","tid":551282,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0c0ccb6e4367e891586ef7e7e056ef33fe7408e","tid":551282,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:09:06.000Z","msg":",4, 巴打!"},{"pid":"492da80c13226ad4a5c85f4ae1e635f72170faba","tid":551282,"uid":122572,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"又好似幾啱"},{"pid":"2c2c3509c37e7e7a8dfd4f7de25c8bd910cbcb01","tid":551282,"uid":152934,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"冷雨夜你老母生癬"},{"pid":"d6398223bfef5ac57b350decea1a155dc7b87d77","tid":551282,"uid":152934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"䦨屎要看清楚 閪汁我沒膽試"},{"pid":"4cab89403565fe4707bcabae095250db49af3a76","tid":551282,"uid":136773,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/000438_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F000438_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=8f7e3097&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f9f0b8b8b8ff4ad67146fd2cc30dee36062f77e","tid":551282,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:05:18.000Z","msg":"含撚醒多$50 少不了"},{"pid":"8169ae179d3524b4cc61a2102c4d6930793c62f7","tid":551282,"uid":136773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T18:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208b92adc7a4c73b10cb417e626562d32b0aff8c","tid":551282,"uid":65473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T19:48:44.000Z","msg":"好似邱騰華"},{"pid":"f4bee88bbc9ef0d74044dc2fe242083f74f1f7e3","tid":551282,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T19:54:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以解釋下"},{"pid":"b85cf9403c4fd0c43819df237c3d3a867f9f315d","tid":551282,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T20:33:45.000Z","msg":"請摸摸我碌鳩"},{"pid":"01ca0a98c3008dd33a6dc8063e2ec9b64410ab68","tid":551282,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"208b92adc7a4c73b10cb417e626562d32b0aff8c","tid":551282,"uid":65473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T19:48:44.000Z","msg":"好似邱騰華"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7ecccadff13206476dc3ee33f9b2151b220116","tid":551282,"uid":4806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"Richard billyham"},{"pid":"0287bff59566ee0d21d6deb396d6e4089eb3590e","tid":551282,"uid":14833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T02:34:56.000Z","msg":"今我等兩日 條撚方可插入 好鳩興"},{"pid":"7ec3fe37fa5142a633c502672a88b7c074577e56","tid":551282,"uid":30478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"47e704546f18e2099b4e0556528dfac091a3593d","tid":551282,"uid":136773,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你侮辱咗首歌</blockquote><br />\n1986年香港殿堂級搖滾樂隊Beyond成員黃家駒，當年為了探索林過雲的思路歷程及對死亡的抽象，創作出了一首叫《Dead romance part2》的歌曲 ，歌詞It's a rainy night/Can you help me/Man, you feel so lonely(這雨夜,你可否來給我救援,你多孤獨),探索了「雨夜屠夫」的心路歷程。<br />\n<br />\n冷雨夜發行於1988年專輯「再見理想」 ﹐歌詞最後一句 <br />\n：雖知要說清楚 可惜我沒膽試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T02:50:53.000Z","msg":"嘩...有幾可見到香港音樂會玩到咁抽象<br />\n仲要好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87e9a569b1f9c64be74339e7bca9b41a6da2319","tid":551282,"uid":136773,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f4bee88bbc9ef0d74044dc2fe242083f74f1f7e3","tid":551282,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T19:54:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以解釋下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"在<span style=\"color: red;\">雨中</span>漫步 <span style=\"color: red;\">藍色街燈漸露</span><br />\n<br />\n林過雲在犯案前為一名值<span style=\"color: red;\">夜班的的士司機</span>，而案件中受害者均為女性。犯案時多為<span style=\"color: red;\">下雨的晚上</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">相對望 無聲緊擁抱著<br />\n為了找往日 尋溫馨的往日</span> 消失了<br />\n<br />\n梁惠心是唯一一名<span style=\"color: red;\">被林過雲姦屍</span>的受害者，再進行肢解拍照錄影，錄影帶名為「第四次行動」。林過雲在聆訊期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">每當問及梁惠心的事情</span>，他曾經<span style=\"color: red;\">數度落淚</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">心更亂 愁絲繞千百段<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">驟變的態度 無心傷她說話 收不了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n林過雲沒有即時殺害梁惠心，只是利刀要脅，並以手銬扣着她雙手，她在長沙灣及葵涌一帶「兜風」數小時，並在車上與死者<span style=\"color: red;\">談論家人、前途等問題</span>，至清晨5時，林過雲才以<span style=\"color: red;\">電線勒死</span>梁惠心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冷雨夜我不想歸家</span><br />\n<br />\n有專家對林過雲的罪行作結論時表示，林過雲是一個備受剝削的人。事實上，<span style=\"color: red;\">林過雲的童年非常不快，在一個複雜的家庭成長</span>，父親有三位太太。林過雲童年時曾經在婆羅乃生活，據他生母所講，林過雲與他爸爸的關係童年時開始已經很差，他爸爸對子女的管教嚴厲，時常對林過雲拳打腳踢。林過雲長大後，雖與家人同住，但關係無改善，他經常逗留於房間內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冷雨夜我在妳身邊<br />\n盼望你會知 可知道我的心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">比當初已改變 只牽強地相處</span><br />\n<br />\n林過雲在法庭上表白殺人心態時說，殺死第一名女子時並無犯罪感，只是被一種憤怒驅使；殺死第二、三名受害人是<span style=\"color: red;\">因為上了癮</span>；當殺到第四個的時候，已經<span style=\"color: red;\">開始厭倦</span>，並自己亦不明所以，因為與梁惠心是相處最久。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怕望妳背影 只苦笑望雨點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">須知要說清楚 可惜我沒膽試</span><br />\n<br />\n林過雲在供詞中表示，他想讓這批女性器官的照片成為歷史圖片，<span style=\"color: red;\">想讓全世界的人都看到他拍的照片</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=loadpdf&amp;t=news&amp;id=3407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Ffi%3Dloadpdf%26t%3Dnews%26id%3D3407&d=A8E5SHWKOxCGSy%2BODRUFMU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=262bf7cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=loadpdf&amp;t=news&amp;id=3407</a>"},{"pid":"368e238301c5a6aa39dc3cf1cfc14b1c2994586a","tid":551282,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e87e9a569b1f9c64be74339e7bca9b41a6da2319","tid":551282,"uid":136773,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f4bee88bbc9ef0d74044dc2fe242083f74f1f7e3","tid":551282,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T19:54:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以解釋下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"在<span style=\"color: red;\">雨中</span>漫步 <span style=\"color: red;\">藍色街燈漸露</span><br />\n<br />\n林過雲在犯案前為一名值<span style=\"color: red;\">夜班的的士司機</span>，而案件中受害者均為女性。犯案時多為<span style=\"color: red;\">下雨的晚上</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">相對望 無聲緊擁抱著<br />\n為了找往日 尋溫馨的往日</span> 消失了<br />\n<br />\n梁惠心是唯一一名<span style=\"color: red;\">被林過雲姦屍</span>的受害者，再進行肢解拍照錄影，錄影帶名為「第四次行動」。林過雲在聆訊期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">每當問及梁惠心的事情</span>，他曾經<span style=\"color: red;\">數度落淚</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">心更亂 愁絲繞千百段<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">驟變的態度 無心傷她說話 收不了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n林過雲沒有即時殺害梁惠心，只是利刀要脅，並以手銬扣着她雙手，她在長沙灣及葵涌一帶「兜風」數小時，並在車上與死者<span style=\"color: red;\">談論家人、前途等問題</span>，至清晨5時，林過雲才以<span style=\"color: red;\">電線勒死</span>梁惠心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冷雨夜我不想歸家</span><br />\n<br />\n有專家對林過雲的罪行作結論時表示，林過雲是一個備受剝削的人。事實上，<span style=\"color: red;\">林過雲的童年非常不快，在一個複雜的家庭成長</span>，父親有三位太太。林過雲童年時曾經在婆羅乃生活，據他生母所講，林過雲與他爸爸的關係童年時開始已經很差，他爸爸對子女的管教嚴厲，時常對林過雲拳打腳踢。林過雲長大後，雖與家人同住，但關係無改善，他經常逗留於房間內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冷雨夜我在妳身邊<br />\n盼望你會知 可知道我的心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">比當初已改變 只牽強地相處</span><br />\n<br />\n林過雲在法庭上表白殺人心態時說，殺死第一名女子時並無犯罪感，只是被一種憤怒驅使；殺死第二、三名受害人是<span style=\"color: red;\">因為上了癮</span>；當殺到第四個的時候，已經<span style=\"color: red;\">開始厭倦</span>，並自己亦不明所以，因為與梁惠心是相處最久。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怕望妳背影 只苦笑望雨點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">須知要說清楚 可惜我